# MessagesGateway API General

This part covers general request such as send message,send email,check status

## Requests collection [/requests]
### send message [POST/message/{contact},{body},{tag},{callback_url}]
 This request is used to send message with some body.
 
 Headers must contain key "Auhtorization" with value "Bearer *token*".
 
 
 Returns  message_id and  tag as a response 
+ Parameters
     + contact: "+380631111111"(String,required),
     + body: "hello"(String,required),
     + tag: "1111111"(String,required),
     + callback_url: "https://www.google.com" (String,optional)

+ Request 

         {"resource": {
             "contact": "+380631111111",      
             "body": "hello",
             "tag": "1111111",
             "callback_url": "https://www.google.com"
          }
          }
         
+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
          "data": {
        "message_id": "ddb576a5-27ca-4502-bdf2-f31f940833de",
        "tag": "1111111"
        },
        "meta": {
        "code": 200,
        "request_id": "2lttqf04g643qgp6oc000cm1",
        "type": "object",
        "url": "http://localhost:4011/message"
        }
        }  

### send email [POST /sending/email/{email},{body},{tag}]
This request is used during email sending .

Headers must contain key "Auhtorization" with value "Bearer *token*".


Returns  message_id and  tag as a response  
+ Parameters
     + email: "u@u.u"(String,required),
     + body: "hello"(String,required),
     + tag: "1111111"(String,required),
     
+ Request 

         {"resource": {
             "email": "u@u.u",      
             "body": "hello",
             "tag": "1111111"
          }
          }     

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
          "data": {
        "message_id": "ddb576a5-27ca-4502-bdf2-f31f940833de",
        "tag": "1111111"
        },
        "meta": {
        "code": 200,
        "request_id": "2lttqf04g643qgp6oc000cm1",
        "type": "object",
        "url": "http://localhost:4011/sending/email"
        }
        }   

### check status [GET /message/{message_id}]
This request is used to check message_status via its message_id.

Headers must contain key "Auhtorization" with value "Bearer *token*".
+ Parameters
      + message_id: "dd830ede-6790-4f66-9ee5-76022640e4eb"(String,required)

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
          "data": {    
         "message_id": "dd830ede-6790-4f66-9ee5-76022640e4eb",
         "message_status": "not_found"

         },
         "meta": {
         "code": 200,
         "request_id": "2lttqf04g643qgp6oc000cm1",
         "type": "object",
         "url": "http://localhost:4011/message/?message_id=dd830ede-6790-4f66-9ee5-76022640e4eb"
         }
         }  
         
